{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PM8uYtGt1hGTfpBWVWC9YH","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Harness Cost Report\n     2→\n     3→Total API-equivalent cost: $896.45\n     4→Total API calls: 6537\n     5→Average cost per story: $4.17 (158 stories)\n     6→\n     7→## Cost by Token Type\n     8→\n     9→| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n    10→|------|--------|------|------|---|\n    11→| Cache reads | 347,550,780 | $1.50/MTok | $521.33 | 58% |\n    12→| Cache writes | 12,514,354 | $18.75/MTok | $234.64 | 26% |\n    13→| Output | 1,870,075 | $75/MTok | $140.26 | 16% |\n    14→| Input | 15,226 | $15/MTok | $0.23 | 0% |\n    15→\n    16→## Cost by Phase\n    17→\n    18→| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n    19→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    20→| verify | 3836 | $476.61 | 53.2% |\n    21→| orchestrator | 910 | $200.74 | 22.4% |\n    22→| retro | 772 | $105.65 | 11.8% |\n    23→| code-review | 400 | $46.34 | 5.2% |\n    24→| create-story | 348 | $37.05 | 4.1% |\n    25→| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 3.4% |\n    26→\n    27→## Cost by Tool\n    28→\n    29→| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n    30→|------|-------|------|---|\n    31→| Bash | 2424 | $297.43 | 33.2% |\n    32→| Read | 1364 | $189.55 | 21.1% |\n    33→| Edit | 1018 | $131.10 | 14.6% |\n    34→| Agent | 635 | $83.01 | 9.3% |\n    35→| Skill | 224 | $77.09 | 8.6% |\n    36→| Grep | 458 | $51.84 | 5.8% |\n    37→| Write | 160 | $28.41 | 3.2% |\n    38→| Glob | 111 | $19.26 | 2.1% |\n    39→| TodoWrite | 111 | $15.24 | 1.7% |\n    40→| ToolSearch | 28 | $3.10 | 0.3% |\n    41→\n    42→## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n    43→\n    44→| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n    45→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    46→| unknown | 1201 | $237.39 | 26.5% |\n    47→| 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch | 648 | $78.78 | 8.8% |\n    48→| 16-7-update-knowledge-and-enforcement-docs | 216 | $25.55 | 2.8% |\n    49→| 1-1-foo | 198 | $24.35 | 2.7% |\n    50→| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 2.6% |\n    51→| 14-4-observability-backend-choice | 192 | $22.13 | 2.5% |\n    52→| 16-8-update-all-tests | 168 | $20.17 | 2.2% |\n    53→| 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability | 121 | $17.10 | 1.9% |\n    54→| 8-2-expand-state-types-for-rust | 84 | $12.67 | 1.4% |\n    55→| 9-5-multi-stack-docs-remaining-consumers | 84 | $11.07 | 1.2% |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Jb8mm4aSoc3MzNYS676j9n","session_id":"208f84a9-573c-4a5f-9f36-d59dfbd54782","uuid":"bde91cce-7a82-4466-add0-46c07c7d90f8","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:26:39.709Z"}
